^I^I^I&nbsp;









MOVSW


No operands


Copy word at DS:[SI] to ES:[DI].
Update SI and DI.Algorithm:



ES:[DI] = DS:[SI]
if DF = 0 then
^I
^ISI = SI + 2
^IDI = DI + 2
^I
^Ielse
^I
^ISI = SI - 2
^IDI = DI - 2
^I



Example:
ORG 100h

CLD
LEA SI, a1
LEA DI, a2
MOV CX, 5
REP MOVSW

RET

a1 DW 1,2,3,4,5
a2 DW 5 DUP(0)



 C Z S O P A 
 unchanged 


TOP
